1. internal corporate information system

  • 데이터 계측 구조에서 실제 작동이 되는 use case 실물을 보여주는 것이 중요
  • data - ai 기반 분석/통제 - 자동화 : 물류, 제작, 품질, 분류, 이동, 저장

2. e2e Process

  • 핵심 프로세스 중에서 ai 적용이 시급한 과제 도출

  • Reading STEP files using python and giving them as input to a neural network

  • Approaching STEP file analysis as a language processing task: A robust and scale-invariant solution for machining feature recognition

  • 핵심 프로세스

  • Order 2 Cash :

  • source : https://www.aaravsolutions.com/realize-the-value-of-order-to-cash-process-a-detailed-outlook/

  • Purchase to Pay (P2P)

  • Idea to Product (I2P)

  • Lead to Customer (L2C)

  • settlement

  • Order to Cash (O2C) Process:

Order Entry: Receiving and recording customer orders.
Order Processing: Verifying product availability and processing the order.
Picking and Packing: Retrieving items from inventory and preparing them for shipment.
Shipping: Sending the products to customers.
Invoicing: Generating invoices for the delivered products or services.
Payment: Receiving and processing payments from customers.

  • Purchase to Pay (P2P) Process:

Requisition: Identifying the need for goods or services and creating a requisition.
Approval: Seeking approvals for the requisition based on organizational policies.
Purchase Order (PO) Creation: Converting approved requisitions into purchase orders.
Goods/Service Receipt: Receiving and verifying the goods or services against the purchase order.
Invoice Matching: Matching supplier invoices with corresponding purchase orders and receipts.
Payment: Processing payments to suppliers based on verified invoices.

  • Idea to Product (I2P) Process:

Idea Generation: Coming up with product or service ideas.
Planning and Design: Planning the details and designing the product or service.
Development: Creating the product or service based on the plan.
Testing: Conducting tests to ensure quality and functionality.
Productization: Launching the product or service to the market.

  • Lead to Customer (L2C) Process:

Lead Generation: Generating potential customer leads.
Contact and Relationship Building: Establishing contact and building relationships with leads.
Quoting and Proposing: Providing quotes or proposals for products or services.
Contract and Closure: Finalizing contracts and closing deals.
Implementation and Maintenance: Delivering products or services and providing ongoing maintenance.

  • Hire to Retire (H2R) Process:

Recruitment: Attracting and hiring qualified employees.
Onboarding: Integrating new employees into the organization.
Performance Management: Evaluating and managing employee performance.
Training and Development: Providing ongoing training and development opportunities.
Retirement or Resignation: Managing employee exits from the organization.

  • Project Lifecycle (PLC) Process:

Initiation: Defining the project’s scope, objectives, and stakeholders.
Planning: Developing a detailed project plan, including resources and timelines.
Execution: Implementing the project plan and carrying out project activities.
Monitoring and Controlling: Tracking project progress, identifying issues, and making adjustments.
Closure: Closing out the project, documenting lessons learned, and obtaining client acceptance.

3. ai 사용이 필요한 업무

  • 4M 영역 : Sensing - Monitoring/Control - Actuator ; automation

예시

  • 설계에서 CAD 모델링 후 PLM을 통하여 모든 데이터를 관리할 때 반복적이며 시간이 소요되는 업무
  • 부품 설계 후 Item code 생성 및 BOM 작성 업무
  • 참고

4. 기업이 주저하는 이유

  1. one-stop service가 되지 않고 : 부분 부분 솔루션을 제시함
  2. 시도하기 앞서 성공에 대한 확신이 없음
    • 개념만 얘기하고
    • 솔루션만 설명
    • 그같은 방법이 해당 기업에서 작동될 지를 스스로 확신하지 못함
  3. 막상 하려고 하면 많은 자원을 필요로 하며 결과를 하기까지 긴 시간이 소요됨

5. 기업에 확신을 주기위해서

  1. 하고자 하는 것에 대한 use-case별로 실증이 있어야 함
  2. 실증을 제시하고 도입 기업 스스로 확신을 갖도록 하며
  3. 여러 질의에 대한 답변은 물론 추진 시에 필요로하는 모든 사항에 대하여 simulation이 가능해야 함
